   118→//! - NIP-13: Proof of Work
   119→//! - NIP-14: Subject Tag in Text Events (email-style subject lines)
   120→//! - NIP-15: Nostr Marketplace (merchant stalls, products, auctions)
   121→//! - NIP-16: Event Treatment (deprecated, moved to NIP-01)
   122→//! - NIP-17: Private Direct Messages (requires `full` feature)
   123→//! - NIP-18: Reposts
